audioreceiver - audio stream receiving utility  

Small utility to get opus stream from udpsink and play it back to
pulsesink. This example is based on gstreamer examples. 

Requirements: libgstreamer1.0-dev

# audioreceiver -h
audioreceiver 
Usage: -p [port] set receiving port

Functionality

audio_in -> audiostreamer -> audioreceiver -> audio_out

